Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分開了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為邪惡帝皇多惡達\N支配了這座山的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.73,0:01:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連彩虹的顏色也變成了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、火美子和武一郎師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊在各界層\N與多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.43,0:01:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊以第七界層為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經把第一界層的\N戰鬥魔神軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二界層的\N妖物魔神軍團打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正和第三界層的\N火炎魔神軍團戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然剩下的\N只有隊長的金希拉十字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但知道了可令\N第三界層的灼熱地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.55,0:02:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恢復原狀的極寒之劍\N在第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便和師傅他們分開\N一個人上到第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那處得到了\N新結識的雪幫手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只差一步\N便能得到極寒之劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七話\N拔不出來的極寒之劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很強的大風雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙也好像走不動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明差少少\N便能得到極寒之劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.60,0:03:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙!\N去到那極光之前要加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.70,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪! 雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼,之後要你吃更多苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起大風雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.17,0:03:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是也真冷呢,魔兵!\N快取些更熱的水來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多路高士蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!是殘酷將軍\N你精神好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用打招呼了\N知道了渡的行蹤了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.96,0:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請交給我吧,殘酷將軍\N我早已布下天羅地網了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那做得很好,但是不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡有一部叫龍神丸的魔神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如你見到的\N資料我已收集了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.91,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是第三界層的\N所也所也那樣的傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.80,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會好好收拾他\N然後再交給殘酷大人你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我便拭目以待了\N多多路高士蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我也可以出人頭地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒渡的話\N便可以升上第七界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以做多惡達大人身邊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.08,0:04:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪! 雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.17,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪! 雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.23,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才明明還是有大風雪啊\N可是很溫暖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.82,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你已不能逃出那裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七界層很近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼變得很舒服了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!是蝴蝶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!是白兔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.43,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白兔!小白兔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.57,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!他上當了\N渡,這樣你便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白兔,等等啊!小白兔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小白兔,過來吧,小白兔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!抓住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事,謝謝你,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.81,0:07:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!可惡的渡\N竟可從那立體影像中逃出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我和你之前\N收拾的傻瓜是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有後著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不斷叫你,你也向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了\N不止何解突然覺得很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到我清醒時已在那冰柱上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龍神丸保護了我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是擊比倫,雪,退後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進退不得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此說明一下擊比倫吧\N各位還記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在第一界層登場的\N擊比倫的改良版
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.71,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安裝了在雪地\N也可以行走的滾輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在第四界層的首領\N多多路高士蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很快便會升上第七界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的末日終於到了,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要隨便胡說\N我才不會在此認輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.80,0:09:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這精氣也到此為止吧\N上吧!擊比倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!西蒙,踏扁他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好,西蒙,上!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一隻西蒙可以做出什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!奇怪珠!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不中呢,真水皮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是頑強的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.92,0:10:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…不要以為這樣便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.01,0:10:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油!西蒙\N差少少便到山頂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!做得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差少少,加油,西蒙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,只差一步\N只差半步,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今…今次是下山呢\N而且很急呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪,不可以向前伸\N重心會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪…雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個不是千人僊人說過的\N一千年一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞撒姆像發出的光線嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的呢\N那麼胡娜拉像會在那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了,找到了,極寒之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼\N來到這裏要稱讚你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是極寒之劍不會交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙,逃啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於出來了嗎?\N受死吧!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.00,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這便是龍神丸嗎\N沒有傳說中的強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,離遠會很不利的\N用接近戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!是機會了,用登龍劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,用龍牙拳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.00,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的武器我全都很清楚\N你什麼也出不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不行了\N我不能自由地動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著用特製合金的牙\N把你送到地獄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西蒙,要救渡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.55,0:16:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!拔劍吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記著啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,全靠西蒙啊\N是嗎?西蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多路士蒙也不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用下一個手段呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,大叔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟被古拿瑪騙了\N在下真愚蠢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N下次一定要好好教訓他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要教訓鳥先生?真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼可憐啊!他是間諜啊\N一直在騙我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是鳥先生不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼不是壞人啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是壞人便不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏不壞啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.20,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生是好人啊\N他是間諜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!龍牙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.34,0:17:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,一點也沒效\N好,用炎龍拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一招,龍雷拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,那麼厚的冰\N就算是龍神丸也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒之劍\N永遠也無法得到手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.99,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千年一次再會的喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連結胡娜拉和亞撒姆的\N美麗的極光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.50,0:18:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…\N胡娜拉真可以見到亞撒姆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個也許是為了冰封一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連亞撒姆也不見的\N胡娜拉的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了,除了力量不夠外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的冷氣\N令我不能活動自如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了,龍神丸\N之後由我來吧,你放我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.70,0:19:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,能令胡娜拉冰封\N的心溶解的只有亞撒姆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.70,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞撒姆?亞撒姆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,真實之鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個了\N這個可以令胡娜拉的冰溶掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要怎樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.42,0:19:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.00,0:20:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟可到此地步呢\N那力量和勇氣值得一讚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰?多惡達的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.60,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此,我是\N多惡達軍團四天王之一殘酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是四天王之一殘惡鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.44,0:21:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是殘豹\N你欺負了我們很多同伴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他們全部都是\N無能的蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你們阻礙我的\N我要取極寒之劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧!小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹什麼?\N難道要點火嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!什麼答中了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?點了火會怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會變燒豬啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒豬?很有趣!\N一點也不有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很吵!靜點啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.15,0:21:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼\N他們是生是死便要看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.42,0:21:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你硬要取極寒之劍的話\N他們便只有變燒豬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要怎樣做?小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.66,0:22:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱啊!

